Jr. wins over Demo Senate questioner"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=-T5TAAAAIBAJ&sjid=2IQDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6919,3477892&dq=jon+huntsman+jr&hl=en |date=20151021192014 }}. ''Deseret News'' (Salt Lake City).</ref>這項任命使他成為了[[美國|美國]]100年以來最年輕的駐外大使<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nga.org/portal/site/nga/menuitem.29fab9fb4add37305ddcbeeb501010a0/?vgnextoid=766e224971c81010VgnVCM1000001a01010aRCRD|title=Utah Governor Jon Huntsman, Jr.|work=Governor's Information|publisher=National Governors Association|accessdate=December 31, 2011|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604144926/http://www.nga.org/portal/site/nga/menuitem.29fab9fb4add37305ddcbeeb501010a0/?vgnextoid=766e224971c81010VgnVCM1000001a01010aRCRD|archivedate=2011年6月4日|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

